reviewText: Sorry, we cannot agree with the prior reviewer. The videography is not the best you'll ever see by any stretch, but it is quite acceptable. The performances more than make up for its deficiencies. Outstanding. Well worth having, and watching again and again.
Wonderful singing! Flott in great form. A couple of great taste and artistry! However, horrible transfer by Kultur as usual. Poor image quality and audio track out of sync! Avoid!!!!!!!!!
